Class EmailTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.emailtemplateservice.model.EmailTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RenderedTemplate

    public class EmailTemplate
extends Object
implements Serializable
    EmailTemplate is an email template, though it could actually be used for anything, identified by a unique key and set to be locale specific if desired
